snippet.title: Best VGM 1116 - Shatterhand - Area G (Missile Command)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 617 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IVCQ-kau7gs
Best VGM 2186 - https://youtu.be/dGF7xsF0DmQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Shatterhand (1991)
Area G (Missile Command)
Iku Mizutani & Kouichi Yamanishi
